es for a second season of eight episodes, which premiered on July 11, 2016.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.variety.com/2015/tv/news/making-of-the-mob-renewed-season-2-amc-1201554472/|title=AMC Renews 'The Making of the Mob' for Season 2 Based in Chicago|last=Wagmeister|first=Elizabeth|date=July 31, 2015|work=Variety|access-date=July 11, 2016}}</ref>
==Overview== {{See also|List of The Making of the Mob episodes}}
===Season 1 (2015)=== {{Main|The Making of the Mob: New York}} The first season, subtitled ''New York'', highlighted [[Lucky Luciano]], his rise in the New York City [[American mafia|Mafia]], and the creation of the [[Five Families]].
===Season 2 (2016)=== {{Main|The Making of the Mob: Chicago}} The second season, subtitled ''Chicago'', focuses on the origin of [[Al Capone]], his [[Chicago Outfit]], and their expansion into the [[Midwestern United States|Midwestern U.S.]]<ref name="Deadline">{{cite web|url=http://www.deadline.com/2015/01/mad-men-final-episodes-premiere-date-making-of-the-mob-miniseries-night-manager-amc-1201346432/|title=AMC Orders 'The West' Docudrama From Robert Redford, Renews 'Making Of The Mob'|last1=Andreeva|first1=Nellie|last2=Patten|first2=Dominic|date=July 31, 2015|website=[[Deadline Hollywood]]|accessdate=July 11, 2016}}</ref>
==Production== On January 10, 2015, AMC ordered the series as a "special event" [[miniseries]] to air in mid-2015.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.deadline.com/2015/01/mad-men-final-episodes-premiere-date-making-of-the-mob-miniseries-night-manager-amc-1201346432/|title=AMC Sets Premiere Date For 'Mad Men' Final Episodes, Orders Mob Miniseries, Confirms Pickup Of 'Night Manager' Mini|last1=Andreeva|first1=Nellie|last2=De Moraes|first2=Lisa|date=January 10, 2015|website=[[Deadline Hollywood]]|accessdate=July 11, 2016}}</ref> On July 31, 2015, two weeks after the series premiere, AMC renewed it for a second season to air in mid-2016.<ref name="Deadline" />
==Reception== The [[The Making of the Mob: New York|first season]] received mixed responses from television critics and a [[Metacritic]] score of 59 out of 100, based on six reviews, indicating "mixed or average reviews".<ref>{{cite web |title=The Making of the Mob: New York|website=Metacritic|accessdate=July 11, 2016|url=http://www.metacritic.com/tv/the-making-of-the-mob-new-york}}</ref> The [[review aggregator]] website [[Rotten Tomatoes]] reported a 40% "rotten" critics rating based on five reviews.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/making-of-the-mob-new-york/s01/|title=The Making of the Mob: New York (2015)|website=Rotten Tomatoes|accessdate=July 11, 2016}}</ref>
